The paper presents a dataset of tasks for training and evaluating optimizers, and explores the use of this dataset for meta-learning hyperparameter search strategies. This work is highly relevant to the field of machine learning, specifically in the areas of optimization and hyperparameter tuning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), and cs.CL (Computation and Language).
